<br>
This one should go to the library.<br>
<br>
My meager contribution, regarding pet heals in a <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> group</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->:<br>
<br>
In accordance with the above, I believe that pet heals are only usefull in the (not so) rare occasions where smelly stuff hit the fan, and the pet is tanking an add. <br>
<br>
In this case, we are not interested in closing the gap, because the pet might have no chance to actually kill the mob. The only thing we want, is the pet to survive long enough so that the tanks can engage the mob.<br>
<br>
Assuming that you need to buy 30 secs for the main tank, and <br>
(the hp of mob &gt; 30*petdps + magenukes for 30 secs)<br>
and<br>
(mobdps*30 &gt; remaining pet hp)<br>
<br>
